TopicTitle: Just a quick question about a mod that I haven't seen around for a good while.

Articles.Content: What ever happened to KW Rocketry? I started KSP in .19 I think, and that was the first mod I ever installed. With 1.0 almost out I was hunting for it and its a no go, What happened to it?

right here http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/51037-0-23-KW-Rocketry-v2-5-6B-Avaliable-working-3m-Docking!-31-12-2013.

EDIT- And yes it says .25 but it works in .90 just fine.
THANK YOU I saw the .25 and assumed... Enough Said except thanks.

Yup...Whenever I look at the first post of a release thread, I usually will then jump to the last few pages of the thread to check on the latest happenings with the mod...usually, you can quickly determine whether a mod works or not with a later game version, even though it's not stated in the OP.
